creating project:
Creating maven Project:
mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.wipro.topgear -DartifactId=Assignment2 -DarchetypeArtifactId= maven-archetype-quickstart -DinteractiveMode=false

Then modified code and added below dependency:
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.apache.commons</groupId>
    <artifactId>commons-lang3</artifactId>
    <version>3.0</version>
</dependency>

While building faced few errors realted java JRE and JDK,but resolved then and compiled aand tested the project.

